author: makortel
body:
Fixes the following warning from scram
```
tmp/slc6_amd64_gcc630/MakeData/DirCache.mk:12514: No such file exists: src/RecoJets/JetProducers/test/test-large-voronoi-area.cc. Please fix src/RecoJets/JetProducers/test/BuildFile.
```
The `test-large-voronoi-area.cc` was removed in #22305, and this `BuildFile.xml` was only instructed to build that.

Tested in 10_1_0_pre3, no changes expected.
title: Remove RecoJets/JetProducers/test/BuildFile.xml as unnecessary
